## ðŸ§© 26. Remove Duplicates from Sorted Array

### Problem Link:
[LeetCode 26](https://leetcode.com/problems/remove-duplicates-from-sorted-array/)

### Code:
```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    int removeDuplicates(vector<int>& nums) {
        int n=nums.size();
        int i=0;
        int j=1;
        while(j<n){
            if(nums[i]!=nums[j]){
                nums[++i]=nums[j];
            }
            j++;
        }
        return i+1;
    }
};
```

