## ðŸ§© 80. Remove Duplicates from Sorted Array II

### Problem Link:
[LeetCode 80](https://leetcode.com/problems/remove-duplicates-from-sorted-array-ii/)

### Code:
```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    int removeDuplicates(vector<int>& nums) {
        int n=nums.size();
        int i=2;
        int k=2;
        if(n<=2) return n;
        while(i<n){
            if(nums[i]!=nums[k-2]){
                nums[k]=nums[i];
                k++;
            }
            i++;
        }
        return k;
    }
};
```

